reviewText: Fast service and nice story for an old Air Force vet.
I got this set of DVD's for my husband, who is an Air Force veteran, and he is really happy with them.

In just a few years air warfare will undergo a revolutionary
change, thanks in part to our  space age technology evolving
at an extraordinary pace. Manned combat aircraft will become
obsolete,  a thing of the past.  Unmanned combat planes will
be controlled by pilots on the ground in front of computer
readouts. providing a low risk, low cost  strike force for our
Air Force and Navy. Information UAVs (Unmanned Air Vehicles)
feed into computers will significantly speed up attacks on
enemy locations.
